Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往生净土非吾所虑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此世之姿我所思兮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丑…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满脸口水!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫干吗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外过夜的时候不是要你提前做好早饭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也来吧
